flavor_text_entries.red:
The large pincer
has 10000 hp of
crushing power. However, its huge
size makes it
unwieldy to use.
flavor_text_entries.blue:
The large pincer
has 10000 hp of
crushing power. However, its huge
size makes it
unwieldy to use.
flavor_text_entries.yellow:
One claw grew
massively and as
hard as steel. It has 10,000-HP
strength. However,
it is too heavy.
flavor_text_entries.gold:
It can hardly
lift its massive,
overgrown pincer. The pincer's size
makes it difficult
to aim properly.
flavor_text_entries.silver:
Its pincers grow
peculiarly large.
If it lifts the pincers too fast,
it loses its bal­
ance and staggers.
flavor_text_entries.crystal:
Its oversized claw
is very powerful,
but when it's not in battle, the
claw just gets in
the way.
flavor_text_entries.ruby:
KINGLER has an enormous, oversized
claw. It waves this huge claw in the
air to communicate with others. However, because the claw is so heavy,
the POKéMON quickly tires.
